  <section class="section_faq">
    <div class="padding-global padding-section-large">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-large w-container">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:2rem;" class="fade-in-bottom">
          <div class="badge"><div class="badge_text"><div>FAQ</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_component">
          <div class="faq_header fade-in-bottom">
            <h2 class="heading-style-h2">Need Help?</h2>
            <a href="/contact" class="text-color-accent" style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:1rem;">Contact us to get an answer</a>
            <img src="/images/harold.png" loading="lazy" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="width:60%;display:block;margin-top:1.5rem;" />
          </div>
          <div class="faq_list fade-in-bottom">
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">Do I have to connect my bank account?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">No — never. Countist is designed to be completely bank-free. You add your subscriptions manually, which keeps your financial credentials 100% private. No Plaid, no read access, no OAuth to your bank.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">Why do you need my credit card for a free trial?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">We don't — no credit card is required to start your free trial. Sign up and get full access for 14 days before you ever need to enter payment information.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">What makes Countist different?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">Most subscription trackers require bank access or read your transaction history. Countist is privacy-first — you enter subscriptions manually. We then apply AI to check prices, detect duplicates and overlaps, and surface smart savings tips based on your actual subscription list.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">Will you cancel subscriptions for me?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">Countist doesn't cancel subscriptions on your behalf — that would require account access we intentionally don't take. What we do is give you clear visibility and direct links so canceling is fast and easy when you decide it's time.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">What happens after my free trial?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">After your 14-day trial, you'll be prompted to subscribe at $4.99/month or $49/year. If you choose not to continue, your account will simply become inactive — no charges, no surprises.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">Is my data secure?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">Yes. Because you enter subscriptions manually, we never hold your banking credentials, transaction history, or login tokens. Your subscription data is encrypted at rest and in transit and is never sold or shared with third parties.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">Can I export my data?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">Yes — data export is included in every plan. Download your full subscription list at any time. Your data is always yours.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq_item">
              <summary class="faq_question">
                <span class="heading-style-h5">What if I have 50 subscriptions?</span>
                <span class="faq_icon-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="faq_answer-text">
                <p class="text-size-regular text-color-secondary">Countist supports unlimited subscriptions on all plans. Whether you have 5 or 500, the dashboard, calendar, and AI tools scale with you — no tiered limits.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

